HEADWORD: Teary
<hw>Tear"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Wet with
tears; tearful.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Consisting of tears, or drops like tears.</def>⟦br⟧
